591
00:32:20,856 --> 00:32:22,190
Which two?

592
00:32:22,273 --> 00:32:23,859
You and Riko.

593
00:32:25,193 --> 00:32:26,945
I wanted to talk to you.

594
00:32:27,863 --> 00:32:30,115
Recently...

595
00:32:31,199 --> 00:32:33,159
Well we talk, right?

596
00:32:34,035 --> 00:32:37,205
About your dates and everything.

597
00:32:37,873 --> 00:32:41,417
And I give advice.

598
00:32:42,711 --> 00:32:45,881
But to be honest, what you're doing...

599
00:32:46,632 --> 00:32:48,842
and what's being said is too different.

600
00:32:50,594 --> 00:32:51,887
There's a gap.

601
00:32:55,181 --> 00:32:59,561
You meet after the rest of us are asleep.

602
00:32:59,645 --> 00:33:04,024
When I ran out of the elevator
the other day,

603
00:33:04,107 --> 00:33:05,984
I saw you guys kissing.

604
00:33:09,863 --> 00:33:13,366
When did you guys start sleeping together?

605
00:33:13,449 --> 00:33:19,122
I noticed you disappearing
about a month ago.

606
00:33:19,998 --> 00:33:23,334
When I'd wake up around 4:00 a.m.

607
00:33:25,211 --> 00:33:28,882
sometimes Riko would be there.

608
00:33:32,010 --> 00:33:37,098
What's the real reason you're doing this?

